title: Tigerstaden
overview: The girls from the TV2 Bliss series Tigerstaden are back with the second season of the popular reality show. Linni Meister, Carina Dahl and Mari Haugersveen are joined in the new episodes of the series by their friend Anette-Marie Antonsen. "Tigerstaden" is a reality show about extremely ambitious girls in Oslo's best west. We follow them in their pursuit of success and love - while they both work and party hard.
